---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import QuoteCTA from "../../components/QuoteCTA.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Live Honeybee Removal & Relocation"
  description="Live, no-kill honeybee removal and relocation in Central Pennsylvania by a working beekeeper. Swarms and established colonies rehomed, not exterminated."
  path="/services/honeybee-removal/"
>
  <section class="section pine-section">
    <div class="wrap"><p class="eyebrow">Service</p><h1>Honeybee Removal</h1>
    <p class="lede">Live removal and relocation by a working beekeeper — bees rehomed, not killed.</p></div>
  </section>
  <section class="section"><div class="wrap prose">
    <h2>Honeybees don't have to be destroyed</h2>
    <p>Honeybees are protected, valuable pollinators. When a swarm settles or a colony moves into a structure, a beekeeper can often remove and relocate them alive — a better outcome for you and for the bees.</p>
    <h2>How it works</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Identification — confirming they're honeybees, not wasps or yellow jackets</li>
      <li>Live removal of swarms or established colonies</li>
      <li>Relocation to a managed apiary</li>
    </ul>
    <!-- ⚠️ If you do NOT offer honeybee removal, delete this file and remove
         the entry in src/data/services.js. -->
  </div></section>
  <QuoteCTA heading="Found a swarm or a colony?" />
</BaseLayout>
<style>.lede{font-size:1.2rem}.prose{max-width:46rem}.prose ul{padding-left:1.2rem}.prose li{margin-bottom:0.5rem}</style>
